name: Dreamin' of everything
description: The way we operate in life is circular. We agree upon that, and yet we deny ourselves seasoning. When I go to bed at night, all I think about is wishing I was out of wherever I am currently. Even when I go somewhere else! But to eat a bagel. No matter the situation- that is liberation.
